🎬 CineGenesis-Core

CineGenesis-Core is the foundational engine of the CineGenesis AI ecosystem — a next-generation multimodal generation system for video, audio, image, and cinematic content creation.

It provides low-level building blocks used by:

cinegenesis-pipelines (inference workflows)
cinegenesis-trainer (training & fine-tuning)
cinegenesis-ui (frontend system)
📦 What's Inside?
🔹 Core Components
components/ → Diffusion modules (Schedulers, Guiders, Noisers, Patchifiers)
conditioning/ → Image, video, keyframe conditioning system
guidance/ → Attention control & cinematic guidance engine
loader/ → Model loader (.safetensors, LoRA fusion, memory optimization)
quantization/ → FP8 optimization for low VRAM usage
🎥 Models
model/transformer/ → Dual-stream CineGenesis Transformer (Video + Audio)
model/video_vae/ → Video encoder/decoder (latent compression)
model/audio_vae/ → Audio latent processing system
model/vocoder/ → Neural audio waveform generator
model/upsampler/ → Resolution enhancement system
🧠 AI Intelligence
text_encoders/ → Advanced multilingual text encoder (Gemma-based)
Separate embeddings for:
Video understanding
Audio synchronization
🚀 Quick Start
# Setup environment
uv sync --frozen

# Activate environment
source .venv/bin/activate

Or install manually:

pip install -e packages/cinegenesis-core
