🔧 Loader System

Load models + LoRA adapters easily:

from cinegenesis_core.loader import SingleGPUModelBuilder

builder = SingleGPUModelBuilder(
    model_path="model.safetensors"
)

model = builder.build(device="cuda")
🔗 LoRA Support
builder = (
    SingleGPUModelBuilder(model_path="model.safetensors")
    .lora("style.safetensors", strength=0.8)
)

