🧠 Architecture Overview

CineGenesis-Core uses a dual-stream cinematic AI architecture:

Text Prompt → AI Encoder
Video → Video VAE → Latents
Audio → Audio VAE → Latents

        ↓

CineGenesis Transformer (Video + Audio Sync)

        ↓

Latents → Video Decoder → Final Video
Latents → Audio Decoder → Final Sound
